                    <ul class="kpi-list">
                        <li>‚Ä¢ Mentorship connections made</li>
                        <li>‚Ä¢ Halal business opportunities created</li>
                        <li>‚Ä¢ Educational content consumption</li>
                        <li>‚Ä¢ Ummah economic impact stories</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
